name: [WEB DEMO] Low Poly Sci Fi Corridor
name_original: [WEB DEMO] Low Poly Sci Fi Corridor
description:
Hello-

This is a web demo to showcase a scene made using low poly modular geometry for sci-fi spaceship interiors.

The asset pack can be purchased here.

Lighting is different as the provided screenshots were made in a standalone build of Unity3D to show off the full range of lighting effects.
